# Public SSH config

## Personal hosts (usernames, internal hostnames) live in ~/.ssh/config.local

Include ~/.ssh/config.local

## Global defaults

Host *
 ServerAliveInterval 60
 ServerAliveCountMax 3
 HashKnownHosts yes
 AddKeysToAgent yes
 ControlMaster auto
 ControlPersist 10m

## Public git forges — identity files only, no usernames

Host github.com
 User git
 PreferredAuthentications publickey
 IdentityFile ~/.ssh/personal_github
 IdentitiesOnly yes

## KM3NeT GitLab

Host git.km3net.de
 User git
 PreferredAuthentications publickey
 IdentityFile ~/.ssh/km3net_gitlab
 IdentitiesOnly yes

Host hf.co
 HostName hf.co
 User git
 IdentityFile ~/.ssh/huggingface
 IdentitiesOnly yes
